articles.author: Lucia Mutikani
articles.title: US weekly jobless claims hit seven-month low - Reuters
articles.description: The number of Americans filing new applications for unemployment benefits fell to a seven-month low last week, suggesting that job growth likely rebounded in November after abruptly slowing last month amid hurricanes and strikes.
